"rationale":"Multiple deposits of INR50,000 or more observed into mule accounts (ACC-MULE-01 to ACC-MULE-06), which then funnelled lumps onward through transactions like TXN-R00011 and TXN-R00023. This classic smurfing strategy is designed to avoid reporting requirements.",
